Chrome extension for Oxford Advanced Learners Dictionary (OALD)

Omnibox:
    Type o <word> in the omnibox to look up the meaning and usage 
    of <word> in OALD website.

Context menu:
    A context menu item "OALD definition of <word>" takes you 
    to the OALD page for the selected <word>. 

Content Script:
    Double click on a word in any page to open the OALD definition 
    page for the word.
